description: This file defines a React component called MindMap, which serves as a placeholder for a visual mind map or roadmap page in a career navigation application. It imports React, as well as common components for section headers and buttons, and renders static content with descriptions about future visualization features.

methods.name: MindMap({ graphData, onSkillStatusChange })
methods.description: React functional component that renders a placeholder for a mind map visualization, accepting graphData and onSkillStatusChange as props.
